headline: Should You Forget Coca-Cola? Why You Might Want to Buy This Unstoppable Growth Stock Instead.
summary: Coca-Cola is one of the dominant consumer staples companies.  Another famous name -- Hershey -- offers a high yield and attractive valuation.  Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) is a great business, but that doesn't mean it is a great stock to own.
